# `data/` is gitignored except `data/pages/` (page PNGs we serve via
# StaticFiles) and `qdrant_local/` (baked vector index). Both flow into
# the image so the deploy needs no external Qdrant or pages service.
# Render via `python -m scripts.render_pages` and ingest via
# `python -m scripts.bootstrap_corpus --qdrant path:./qdrant_local` before
# `docker build`.
